7.1992, 147.3445, 146.9176, 147.835, 147.1358, 149.4622, 149.4958, 149.2872, 150.7143, 151.0961, 150.772, 151.8361, 149.3048, 149.6614, 150.7646, 151.2565, 150.5816, 150.5419, 151.1347, 151.2154, 151.2209, 152.1846, 152.055, 152.2028, 153.3345, 153.0268, 153.2542, 152.77, 152.4487, 152.5151, 152.8391, 153.9948, 154.855, 155.6938, 157.8187, 160.6836, 158.1918, 158.4646, 157.9083, 157.0478, 156.2194, 156.0115, 155.7649, 155.8152, 155.9246, 156.2951, 157.8462, 156.0238, 155.2202, 156.1441, 156.9159, 156.7473, 157.4559, 158.2139, 159.2455, 159.1934, 159.9523, 159.891, 160.0622, 160.7876, 160.9237, 160.7538, 160.4309, 159.9076, 159.1781, 158.8581, 158.9147, 158.0225, 158.5981, 157.7588, 157.7413, 157.2962, 157.7107, 157.5545, 157.1176, 156.1916, 155.7356, 157.3222, 157.9526, 157.45, 158.5139, 157.779, 155.2358, 156.4517, 155.2973, 153.6275, 153.218, 154.0087, 153.9157, 153.0896, 153.4046, 154.4866, 155.569, 156.3372, 156.8949, 156.905, 156.6024, 156.9783, 156.5052, 156.5558, 157.8149, 157.4984, 156.7857, 157.0485, 156.8343, 157.0244, 157.4068, 156.9503, 155.0954, 155.9985, 156.3986, 155.7909, 155.372, 155.1152, 155.5056, 155.6839, 155.2386, 154.6119, 154.6933, 154.2408, 155.0103, 154.7336, 154.7358, 154.4543, 154.7382, 154.481, 154.4109, 154.8402, 154.5617, 154.9255, 155.2191, 154.8901, 155.5129, 155.4872, 154.9403, 157.203, 157.9874, 159.5635, 159.4517, 160.1313, 160.1074, 160.182, 159.5668, 157.9821, 158.699, 159.5553, 157.9909, 158.1991, 158.9473, 158.3787, 158.5101, 158.5002, 158.7027, 160.2895, 159.1125, 158.6086, 157.8672, 159.3099, 160.8576, 160.4156, 160.2307, 161.701, 161.9087, 159.5828, 160.7299, 161.8322, 162.74, 162.043, 163.134, 163.202, 165.2012, 164.5444, 167.3119, 167.1216, 167.8447, 166.7382, 166.7628, 166.8415, 169.272, 168.5379, 169.171, 169.3235, 168.8838, 169.2999, 169.3721, 170.9277, 170.6117, 169.3246, 170.2264, 169.5473, 170.8833, 167.8302, 168.2025, 168.6349, 168.1027, 168.2361, 167.0318, 167.1485, 165.5085, 164.1972, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null], "summary_html": "<h1>基差EMA时序偏离度因子</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本因子捕捉商品期货基差（期现价差）的时序异常偏离。核心思路是：基差反映市场对未来供需的预期，当某品种基差显著偏离其历史均值时，存在回归或持续的交易机会。具体做法是对日频 <code>basis</code> 字段做 EMA 平滑以消除短期噪声，再计算滚动 Z-score 衡量偏离程度，最后在截面上用排名归一化转为连续仓位信号。做多基差异常高（backwardation 加深）的品种、做空基差异常低（contango 加深）的品种。</p>\n<p>该因子的突出优点是极低的换手率（日均约 36%）和良好的 OOS 泛化能力，与现有因子库的最大相关性仅 0.42，提供了有效的增量信息。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.12</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>4.7%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.2%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-6.5%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.02</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>2886</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.15</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>2.02</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.27 / 1.08</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.91</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.51</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.46</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.5</span></td><td>1.47</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.13</span></td><td>0.76</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.53</span></td><td>1.55</td><td>1.27</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.05</span></td><td>0.69</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.86</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>basis</code></td><td>基差</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 15 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 15 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>50</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>2888</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>98.5%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>39.9</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{basis\\_ema}_t = \\text{EMA}(\\text{basis}, S)_t</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">z_t = \\frac{\\text{basis\\_ema}_t - \\mu(\\text{basis\\_ema}, W)_t}{\\sigma(\\text{basis\\_ema}, W)_t}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position}_t = \\text{rank\\_to\\_continuous}\\left(\\text{cr\\_rank}(z_t)\\right)</div>\n<p>其中：</p>\n<ul><li><span class=\"math-tex\">S</span> = EMA 平滑窗口（span），最优值 350</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">W</span> = Z-score 滚动窗口，最优值 252</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\mu, \\sigma</span> = 滚动均值和标准差</li>\n<li><code>cr_rank</code> = 截面百分位排名 [0, 1]</li>\n<li><code>rank_to_continuous</code> = 排名映射到 [-1, 1] 连续信号</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p><strong>R1 (Sharpe 0.97)</strong>: 初始实现了完整的因子逻辑，同时探索了两种截面归一化方式（L2+L1 vs cr_rank）和多个 EMA/ZS 参数组合。发现 cr_rank 归一化（Sharpe 0.97）显著优于原始的 L2+L1 归一化（Sharpe 0.70-0.72），原因是 L2+L1 归一化使仓位量级极小导致收益被稀释。ema=350, zs=252 为最优单参数组合。</p>\n<p><strong>R2 (Sharpe 0.97)</strong>: 诊断发现 R1 最优变体换手率偏高（0.53），添加 rebalance_hold 降低换手。hold=10 和 hold=5 的变体略微提升了 Sharpe（从 0.9695 到 0.9717）。同时测试了 3-span 信号平均（ensemble）和 sym_rolling_ic_gate 品种过滤，两者均未带来显著提升。_cs（截面标准化）变体也表现不错（0.88-0.90），但不及 _raw。</p>\n<p><strong>R3 (Sharpe 1.01)</strong>: 进一步细化 hold 参数，发现 hold=15 是甜点，将 Sharpe 从 0.97 提升到 1.01。关键转折点是更长的持仓周期进一步降低了换手率（从 0.39 到 0.36），节省的交易成本直接转化为净收益提升。同时确认 ema=350 仍然是最优 EMA 参数，ema=375/400 略弱。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>数据字段</strong>: <code>basis</code>（期现基差，非空率约 28%）</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种商品期货（约 50 个品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 中长期（hold=15 天再平衡）</li>\n<li><strong>与因子库相关性</strong>: max_corr = 0.42（与 <code>20150508_paper_inv_basis_h40_ts</code> 最相似）</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>: </li>\n</ul>  - basis 字段非空率仅 28%，部分品种数据缺失较多\n<p>- 2016 年和 2024-2025 年 Sharpe 为负，信号在某些市场环境下失效 - JM(焦煤)、RU(橡胶) 为持续负贡献品种，可考虑品种过滤进一步优化</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>ZS_MIN_PERIODS</code></td><td><code>max(60, ZS_WINDOW // 3)</code></td><td>match Polars: max(60, zs_window // 3)</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.18s</li>\n</ul>"}